    <body>

      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">column</rs> plinth</rs>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>Inscribed on the lowest face of the moulding of the socle, which is broken away on both sides.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03–0.035</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0600" cert="low" exact="none" notBefore="0401">Fifth to sixth century</date>, or later (<rs type="criteria">content</rs>, <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
		<ab>
		<lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" extent="10" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost"><w lemma="ὑπέρ">ὑπὲρ</w></supplied> <w lemma="σωτηρία"><supplied reason="lost">σωτ</supplied><unclear reason="damage">η</unclear>ρίας</w> <w lemma="ὁ">το<hi rend="superscript">ῦ</hi></w> <w lemma="ἀρχιεπίσκοπος">ἀρχ<hi rend="superscript">ι</hi><unclear reason="damage">ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost">πισκόπου</supplied></w> <gap dim="right" extent="10-15" unit="character" reason="lost"/></ab>
      </div>

      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
        <p>The restoration, by which I am persuaded, is that of Angelos Chaniotis.</p><p><foreign lang="grc">Η</foreign> might be <foreign lang="grc">Ψ</foreign>,<foreign lang="grc">Δ</foreign>, <foreign lang="grc">ΕΙ</foreign>.</p>
        <p>At the end,<foreign lang="grc">Ε</foreign> might be <foreign lang="grc">Θ</foreign>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">For the salvation</supplied> of <gap reason="lost"/> the <seg cert="low">chief</seg>, <note place="not specified" anchored="yes">or</note> the archbishop <gap dim="right" reason="lost"/></ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="VII.18">VII.18</xref>.</p>
      </div>

